Interface Session

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Endpoint, Extendable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ProtonJSession
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SessionImpl

    public interface Session
extends Endpoint
    Session Note that session level flow control is handled internally by Proton.
